about.description:
A Python package to easily create, manage, and connect to Dask deployments
using Coiled Cloud.
about.summary: Deploy Dask cluster using Coiled Cloud

name: coiled
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "coiled" %}
{% set version = "0.0.7" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 498f02c2e2bda0122088f60f1826efcf15f0a21c7a604411bf7e7fee2538c3ce

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - aiohttp
    - aiobotocore >=0.12.0,<0.13
    - distributed >=2.19.0

test:
  requires:
    - pip
  commands:
    - pip check
  imports:
    - coiled

about:
  home: https://coiled.io
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Deploy Dask cluster using Coiled Cloud'

  description: |
    A Python package to easily create, manage, and connect to Dask deployments
    using Coiled Cloud.
  doc_url: https://coiled.io/cloud

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jrbourbeau
    - mrocklin
